
<section class="intro">
<h2>Image Storage & Reference</h2>
<p>This page serves as a temporary holding area for images used
throughout the site.
Photos uploaded here are organized, reviewed, and then placed into
their proper trade or gear categories.
This section is not part of the public-facing content — it’s simply
a workspace to keep track of images before they are assigned to the
correct pages.
</p>

<p>If an image appears here, it means it’s waiting to be sorted,
renamed, or added to a specific trade page, gear category, or
consumables section.
Once placed, the image will be removed from this page to keep
things clean and organized.
</p>
</section>
